### 1. 管理员登录
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

username=admin&password=123456

### 2. 获取用户信息（需要先登录拿到token）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/auth/info
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiIxIiwicm9sZSI6ImFkbWluIiwiaWF0IjoxNzc4NTU2NzA1LCJleHAiOjE3NzkxNjE1MDV9.wii1npmf1UKSAE-4Vc7zQ0kkyv2NirnpBlDL3RYvUak

### 3. 提交报修（把token换成你自己的）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/order/submit
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiIxIiwicm9sZSI6ImFkbWluIiwiaWF0IjoxNzc4NTU2NzA1LCJleHAiOjE3NzkxNjE1MDV9.wii1npmf1UKSAE-4Vc7zQ0kkyv2NirnpBlDL3RYvUak

{
  "dormId": 1,
  "faultTypeId": 1,
  "description": "水龙头坏了，一直漏水",
  "imageUrls": "/upload/1.jpg"
}

### 4. 查看我的报修
GET http://localhost:8080/api/order/my
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiIxIiwicm9sZSI6ImFkbWluIiwiaWF0IjoxNzc4NTU2NzA1LCJleHAiOjE3NzkxNjE1MDV9.wii1npmf1UKSAE-4Vc7zQ0kkyv2NirnpBlDL3RYvUak

### 5. 管理员查看全部工单
GET http://localhost:8080/api/order/all

### 6. 师傅接单
POST http://localhost:8080/api/order/accept/1
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiIxIiwicm9sZSI6ImFkbWluIiwiaWF0IjoxNzc4NTU2NzA1LCJleHAiOjE3NzkxNjE1MDV9.wii1npmf1UKSAE-4Vc7zQ0kkyv2NirnpBlDL3RYvUak

### 7. 师傅完工
POST http://localhost:8080/api/order/complete/1

### 8. 学生评价
POST http://localhost:8080/api/order/evaluate/1?star=5
